Message.Title: Sharp in talk with Dell for a stake in Sharp.
Message.Msg: Sharp Corp. is in discussions with U.S. technology companies to bolster its battered balance sheet and has offered a stake to Dell Inc. DELL -0.61% , among others, in return for a stable supply of breakthrough display technology, according to people familiar with the discussions.
